Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.51,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决 断 之 时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西也很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧大人 有客人找您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦 让他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧「大人」？ 真臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然随便打开我的货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候变成得这么了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我让他们这么干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「将这个地球打造成我等的理想乡」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第二个阿瓦隆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「别犹豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝在加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾米在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘舰团的人到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都像幽灵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神都像被附身了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的居民肯定也会被变成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如此 我当初离开加尔刚蒂亚又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘愿这样下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在打算谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是来接我的冲浪龙虾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海贼拉凯奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就跟那个龙虾合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙想指望破废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过雷德那家伙不会帮忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就得这样过一辈子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把帆布展开来收集雨水」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你湿透了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「会感冒的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前观测到的称为「雨」的气象现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未感知到特殊异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神赐予了我们巨大的恩典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将前往神的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上至高的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为生者而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为救赎人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而永垂不朽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是为了看这些…而来到这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个疯狂的舰团接下来将驶向加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙我果然受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了从希迪亚斯手中保护大家才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护艾米 为了保护贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护那些人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库盖尔中校发令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雷德少尉进入临战态势」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「听从我的指挥」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请贵官进行判断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判断 你执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我或许从未真正做出过选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解贵官的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校的指令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 你和Striker的战力差有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据不足 无法计算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解贵官的提问意图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够和Striker战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Striker X3752目前的行为不属于同盟的军务范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以认定为交战对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我能和中校战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对该问题的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已超出本机作为驾驶员支援启发系统的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何情况下 战斗方针的制定均交由贵官判断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 使用无线会被拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接传达给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么重大的使命 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能飞往加尔刚蒂亚的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 拯救大家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可欠我一个人情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 进入临战态势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔…刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔刚蒂亚…要被袭击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人开着冲浪风筝飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能听梅露蒂的 改变航路进行避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的立场 不得不这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德让我们逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算自己去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算代替我们 一个人去战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了保护加尔刚蒂亚 甚至不惜和过去的同伴反目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们却要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他作出了选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须作出选择才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 该是使用那把钥匙的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身负舰团贤者之任的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依据职责建议舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是使用之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 希望你也能助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为让世界领略我伟大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领略伟大的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布 新的圣战就此打响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将会得到胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为给这个星球带来绝对的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为将这个星球建设成安宁华贵的理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从于我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是通往恒久幸福的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 这玩笑可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是同盟战士该有的发言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是银河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是人类居住的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的未来是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球上有着活在这里的人们所建立的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有理由破坏它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等的正义不变」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「别犹豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 这是神之间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力怎么会这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测其威力并非来源于内部发生器 而来源于外部装备的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保存自身能量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 给这颗星球带来新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你快撤 这是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们也不怎么讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个装神弄鬼的玩意更让人不爽一万倍！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一发 准备好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不参战的普通居民在装甲区域内躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船是本舰团的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能成为攻击目标 请做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饶恕叛乱 反抗的全都是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我就是这么粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你还挺男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我踹开他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以在战略上确保有利地位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议采取打即跑战术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.98,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(724,650)}Hit-and-run Tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击敌机头部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀死中校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机的机动性凌驾于本机之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「无论强者还是弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「均依靠自身的理性相互扶持」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这才能称为人类吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生器 以最大功率输出！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我说 雷德」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愿不愿意与我一起改变这个星球？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始接近敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入紧急开仓信号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还好有你在」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 还愿意 跟随我…吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿势控制系统 重启
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 贵官的抵抗是毫无意义的
